data.description: NO RESTRICTIONS!!! Calling all buyers looking for land! Welcome to your own piece of paradise in Salado. This remarkable home sits on 10 sprawling acres, offering unparalleled opportunities to witness breathtaking sunsets every evening. Step inside and be greeted by high-vaulted ceilings, ample windows framing beautiful views, and unique features that set this home apart. The well-equipped kitchen features stainless steel appliances, a convenient double oven, a kitchen island, a generously-sized pantry, and a dedicated dining area. When it's time to unwind, the primary suite offers the ultimate sanctuary with its soaring ceilings, a full bath, and a dual vanity. The true heart of this property lies within its vast grounds. Sturdy fencing accommodates livestock, and cross fencing allows for convenient animal separation across well-maintained pastures. Equine enthusiasts will be thrilled with the spacious 5-stall horse barn, complete with a well-appointed tack room, all built on a sturdy concrete slab. Embrace your passion for riding with the meticulously lit roping arena, perfect for both practice and entertainment. The property also features an in-ground pool and hot tub, creating the perfect space to relax and socialize with guests. Don't miss this extraordinary opportunity to own a home that captures the essence of natural beauty and offers a multitude of amenities. Experience the serenity and splendor of this remarkable property by scheduling a showing today!
